Place test file here, and run `go test -v ./...`

The testing program automatically searches for and tests all files named `test*.<ext>`

Such as

- test.anm
- test.arc
- test.col
- test.mate
- test.menu
- test.model
- test.nei
- test.phy
- test.pmat
- test.preset
- test.psk
- test.tex
- test2.anm
- test2.tex
- test231.menu
